Symbol.Script_3D:
IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW OFF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_resol=6
pen gs_cont_pen
unID = 1 for i=1 to 4 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx+tbtt, unID, temp_RR, 1+128 :unID=unID+1 hotspot a/2, 0, zzyzx+tbtt, unID, temp_RR, 2 :unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, zzyzx+tbtt, unID, temp_RR, 3 :unID=unID+1 rotz 90 next i
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 :unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx+tbtt, unID, zzyzx, 2 :unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 :unID=unID+1
!! LEGS resol max(4, int(gs_resol/2)) material gs_leg_mat
tiltAngle = ATN((1-0.725)*zzyzx/(a/2-a/10-a/100)) for i=1 to 4 addy a/2-a/10 cylind zzyzx,ls addz 0.725*zzyzx rotx 90-tiltAngle cylind (1-0.725)*zzyzx/sin(tiltAngle),ls/3 del 3 rotz 90 next i
addz zzyzx
material gs_top_mat resol gs_resol
if stt=0 then valt= int(A/.10) add -a/2,-b/2+.1,0
for i=1 to valt-1 cutpolya 4, 2, 0, 0,0,15, a,0,15, a,.01,15, 0,.01,15 addy .1 next i del i endif
cylind tbtt,a/2
if stt=0 then for i=1 to valt-1 cutend next i endif
material edmat roty -90 rotx -90
if ets_m = 1 then ! no special edge else if ets_m = 2 then revolve 3,360,0, 0,a/2,1, 1/2",a/2,901, 1",a/2,3001 else revolve 4,360,0, 0,a/2,0, 0,a/2+1/6",0, 1",a/2+1/6",0, 1",a/2,0 endif endif
del top
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 7, unID = 3000
unID=1 pen gs_cont_pen line_type gs_line_type circle2 0,0,a/2
fill gs_fill_type POLY2_B 2, 2+64,gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,901, a/2,360,4001
HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,0,180 HOTARC2 0,0,A/2,180,360
!!! ********************** Hotspots
HOTSPOT2 0,0,unID : unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1
ROT2 90 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ROT2 180 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
ROT2 270 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, temp_RR, 1+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, temp_RR, 3+128, A: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 temp_RR, 0, unID, temp_RR, 2, A: unID=unID+1 DEL 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0 values "A" range [8*ls, ) values "B" range [8*ls, )
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif
values "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=4 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol" IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_resol", "gs_shadow"
values "ets" `Без Окантовки`,`Закругленный`,`С Фаской` values "ets_m" 1, 2, 3 if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "ets" then if ets = `Без Окантовки` then ets_m = 1 if ets = `Закругленный` then ets_m = 2 if ets = `С Фаской` then ets_m = 3 parameters ets_m = ets_m else if ets_m = 1 then ets = `Плоский` if ets_m = 2 then ets = `Закругленный` if ets_m = 3 then ets = `С Фаской` parameters ets = ets endif
if ets = `Без Окантовки` then lock "edmat" endif
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "temp_RR" then ! hidden parameter for hotspot editing A = temp_RR*2 B = temp_RR*2 parameters A = A, B = B else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then ! B parameter input A = B temp_RR = B/2 parameters A = A, temp_RR = temp_RR else ! A parameter input B = A temp_RR = A/2 parameters B = B, temp_RR = temp_RR endif endif
!!! ******************************** Minimal Space VALUES "MSFront" RANGE [0,)
Symbol.Comment: Круглый стол, столешница сплошная или из нескольких досок, минимальное пространство.
